'''Horace Pauleus Sannon''' (7 April 1870 - 1938 [[Pétion-Ville]]) was a [[Haiti]]an historian and politician. Born in [[Les Cayes]], Pauleus Sannon studied social-political sciences in [[Paris]], [[France]]. He wrote several books on the history of Haiti, including ''Essai Historique sur la Révolution de 1843'' and ''Histoire de [[Toussaint Louverture]]''.
==Political career== He was a presidential candidate in 1926 and 1930.<ref name="LN">{{cite web|title=Horace Pauléus Sannon, cet illustre inconnu|url=http://lenouvelliste.com/lenouvelliste/article/122709/Horace-Pauleus-Sannon-cet-illustre-inconnu|website=Le Nouvelliste|publisher=Le Nouvelliste|accessdate=19 October 2017}}</ref>
==Works== * ''Haïti et le régime parlementaire'' * ''Un journaliste sous Boyer: Darfour'' (1898) * [http://ufdc.ufl.edu/AA00008866/00001/ ''Histoire de Toussaint Louverture'' Volume 1] * [http://ufdc.ufl.edu/AA00008866/00002/ ''Histoire de Toussaint Louverture'' Volume 2] * [http://ufdc.ufl.edu/AA00008866/00003/ ''Histoire de Toussaint Louverture'' Volume 3]
